I don’t do UI and unless you use re-frame you shouldn’t either. Currently I’m fighting financial crime @ Quantexa This blog is written in emacs + ox-hugo

item.title: Index Common Crawl with Elasticsearch without a running cluster
item.description: Common Crawl is an amazing project I’m always surprised when people I talk to are unfamiliar with Common Crawl, it’s one of the most surprising and empowering projects in a world where governments and corporations seem hell bent on taking power away from us. The projects is host to 8 year of web data grouped in 3 main categories: raw web page, metadata extracts and text extracts with derivative work such as a file index as well as a link graph with ranking for top domains and every page.
